ed as a benchmark\ntest for eclipse modeling and analysis routines, and propose criteria to verify\neclipse detections.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Feb 2013 21:40:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
