rast,\nour result shows that these folded algebraic-geometric codes {\\em themselves}\nhave the claimed list decoding property.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Feb 2013 04:38:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-02-28"}
